<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent58babb15945d42f78bf451b2be39e926">
</div>
<p>West Midlands Hospital is one of the leading <a href="http://www.westmidlandshospital.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="West midlands private hospital">private hospitals</a> in the Birmingham area with an excellent reputation for delivering high quality healthcare for self pay/insured and NHS patients. It is set in 3.5 acres of pleasant grounds at Colman Hill, Halesowen, ten miles from Birmingham City Centre.</p>
<p><br/>By investing in advanced medical technology, the hospital offers a wide range of <a href="http://www.westmidlandshospital.co.uk/treatments.aspx" target="_blank" title="Healthcare treatments in Birmingham">treatments</a>. Please click the <a href="/Services/hospitals/Services/DefaultView.aspx?id=408" target="_self" title="Choose and book services">departments and services</a> for treatments available on Choose and Book.</p>
<p>The fully equipped ultra clean air theatre suite comprises two operating theatres with laminar air flow. These are particularly suitable for Orthopaedic surgery such as arthroscopy, hip and knee replacements and spinal surgery.</p>
<p>We have excellent levels of cleanliness and have effective infection control methods resulting in very low infection rates. All our facilities are regularly inspected and approved by the Care Quality Commission.</p>
<p>Free car parking and disabled access is also available.</p>
<p>Our consultants and nursing staff are highly experienced and have your care and comfort as their highest priority. During and after treatment, you will receive a standard of care which is second to none and all patients have the reassurance that theatre, paramedical services and a resident RMO is available 24 hours a day.</p>
<p>West Midlands Hospital also provides private hospital treatments including full diagnostic and endoscopy procedures, <a href="http://www.ramsayhealth.co.uk/weight-loss-surgery" target="_blank">weight loss surgery</a>, orthopaedic surgery including spinal treatment, <a href="http://www.westmidlandshospital.co.uk/treatments/physiotherapy.aspx" target="_blank" title="Physiotherapy in West Midlands">physiotherapy</a>, <a href="http://www.westmidlandshospital.co.uk/treatments/shockwave-therapy.aspx" target="_blank" title="Shockwave treatments ">shockwave therapy</a> and <a href="http://www.westmidlandshospital.co.uk/cosmetic-surgery.aspx" target="_blank" title="cosmetic surgery in the West Midlands">cosmetic surgery.</a></p>
